{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775812869239,"sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","part":{"id":"prt_d76b1f8c4001HHZQWuU3Fxvf4r","messageID":"msg_d76b1f12c001qvnaDsewV5XSgC","sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_41fafbe5fada4d56b4973501","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: 从 AR-001（AgentRuntime）和 AR-002（CodeInterpreter）中提取并规范化共享类型与常量，建立 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` 包中跨 CRD 复用的类型基座。\n5: \n6: ## 元信息\n7: - **Module**: pkg/apis\n8: - **Language**: Go\n9: - **Size**: S\n10: \n11: ## 目的\n12: AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 两个 CRD 共享 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` 等类型定义。当前这些共享类型定义在 `codeinterpreter_types.go` 中，`agent_type.go` 通过同包隐式引用。本变更将共享类型与常量从具体 CRD 类型文件中解耦，形成独立的 `shared_types.go` 文件，确保：\n13: \n14: 1. **单一数据源** — 共享类型有且仅有一份定义，位置明确\n15: 2. **语义清晰** — 文件名 `shared_types.go` 明确表达\"跨 CRD 共享\"的意图\n16: 3. **可扩展性** — 后续新增 CRD（如 Workflow、Pipeline 等）可直接引用共享类型，无需重复定义或猜测类型位置\n17: 4. **代码生成友好** — `controller-gen` 和 `k8s.io/code-generator` 对同包内的类型无感知差异，提取后不影响 DeepCopy 和 client-go 生成\n18: \n19: ## 范围\n20: \n21: ### 包含\n22: 1. **共享类型定义** — `TargetPort` struct、`ProtocolType` string enum 及其常量\n23: 2. **共享枚举常量** — `AuthModeType` string enum 及其常量（`picod`、`none`）\n24: 3. **新文件创建** — `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n25: 4. **引用迁移** — 从 `codeinterpreter_types.go` 中移除 `ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType`、`TargetPort` 的定义，确保 `agent_type.go` 和 `codeinterpreter_types.go` 通过同包引用共享类型\n26: 5. **单元测试** — 共享类型常量值验证、零值行为测试、DeepCopy 隔离测试\n27: \n28: ### 不包含\n29: - 新增 CRD 类型定义\n30: - CRD YAML 文件生成\n31: - client-go 代码生成（`make gen-client` 不受影响，同包内移动）\n32: - Controller/Reconciler 实现\n33: - 跨 API Group 的共享类型（如未来需要跨 `runtime` 和 `workflow` group 共享，需另行设计）\n34: \n35: ## 共享类型概要\n36: \n37: ```\n38: shared_types.go\n39: ├── ProtocolType (string enum)\n40: │   ├── ProtocolTypeHTTP  = \"HTTP\"\n41: │   └── ProtocolTypeHTTPS = \"HTTPS\"\n42: ├── AuthModeType (string enum)\n43: │   ├── AuthModePicoD = \"picod\"\n44: │   └── AuthModeNone  = \"none\"\n45: └── TargetPort (struct)\n46:     ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n47:     ├── name: string (optional)\n48:     ├── port: uint32 (required)\n49:     └── protocol: ProtocolType\n50: ```\n51: \n52: ### 消费方\n53: \n54: | CRD | 使用的共享类型 | 字段路径 |\n55: |-----|---------------|----------|\n56: | AgentRuntime | `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType` | `Spec.Ports []TargetPort` |\n57: | CodeInterpreter | `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType` | `Spec.Ports []TargetPort`, `Spec.AuthMode AuthModeType` |\n58: \n59: ## 影响分析\n60: \n61: ### 直接影响\n62: | 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n63: |------|------|------|\n64: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | 新增 | 共享类型与常量定义文件 |\n65: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | 修改 | 移除 `ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType`、`TargetPort` 定义（迁移至 shared_types.go） |\n66: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` | 无变更 | 同包引用，无需修改 import |\n67: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | 更新 | `controller-gen object` 重新生成，`TargetPort` 的 DeepCopy 方法位置不变（同包） |\n68: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types_test.go` | 新增 | 共享类型单元测试 |\n69: \n70: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n71: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n72: |------|----------|\n73: | 新增 CRD 类型 | 可直接引用 `shared_types.go` 中的类型，无需重复定义或从 CRD 特定文件中借用 |\n74: | CLI/SDK | 通过共享类型统一端口和协议枚举值，避免不同 CRD 的枚举值不一致 |\n75: | 控制器 | 处理多 CRD 时使用统一的类型，减少类型转换 |\n76: \n77: ### 无影响的组件\n78: - Router（session-routing）— 不直接依赖 CRD 类型定义\n79: - Session Store（Redis/Valkey）— 存储层独立于 API 类型\n80: - Agentd（idle cleanup）— 通过 store 接口交互，不消费 CRD Go 类型\n81: - PicoD（code execution）— 沙箱内组件，与 CRD 定义无关\n82: - client-go 生成代码 — 同包内类型移动不影响 code-generator 的输出\n83: - Makefile — `generate`、`gen-crd`、`gen-client` 目标无需修改\n84: \n85: ## 备选方案\n86: \n87: ### 方案 A：提取到 `shared_types.go`（已选）\n88: **优点**：符合 Kubernetes 项目惯例（如 `k8s.io/api/core/v1/types.go` 中包含多种共享类型）；同包内引用无需修改 import；`controller-gen` 和 code-generator 无感知；文件名明确表达意图；与 AR-001/AR-002 的文件组织风格一致。\n89: **缺点**：如果未来出现跨 API Group 的共享需求，需要额外的 common 包设计。\n90: \n91: ### 方案 B：保留在 `codeinterpreter_types.go` 中（当前状态）\n92: **优点**：无需文件移动；同包引用已经工作。\n93: **缺点**：语义不清晰 — `ProtocolType`、`TargetPort` 并非 CodeInterpreter 独有，放在其类型文件中暗示了错误的归属关系；新增 CRD 开发者可能不知道去哪里找共享类型；违反单一职责原则。**否决**。\n94: \n95: ### 方案 C：创建独立的 `pkg/apis/common/` 包\n96: **优点**：更清晰的公共 API 边界；支持跨 API Group 复用。\n97: **缺点**：当前只有一个 API Group（`runtime`），过早抽象；需要在 `go.mod` 中引入额外的 import 路径；`controller-gen` 需要配置多包扫描；增加维护复杂度。可在未来出现第二个 API Group 时再考虑。**否决**。\n98: \n99: ### 方案 D：使用 Go interface 定义共享行为而非具体类型\n100: **优点**：更灵活的抽象。\n101: **缺点**：Kubernetes CRD 生态依赖具体 struct 类型进行 JSON 序列化、DeepCopy 生成和 client-go 代码生成；interface 无法被 `controller-gen` 识别为 CRD 字段类型；与 Kubernetes API 设计模式不兼容。**否决**。\n102: \n103: ## 验收标准\n104: 1. `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n105: 2. `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType` 在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 中有且仅有一份定义（位于 `shared_types.go`）\n106: 3. `ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`ProtocolTypeHTTPS == \"HTTPS\"`\n107: 4. `AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`、`AuthModeNone == \"none\"`\n108: 5. `TargetPort` 的 DeepCopy 方法在 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 中正确生成\n109: 6. `agent_type.go` 和 `codeinterpreter_types.go` 正常引用共享类型，编译无警告\n110: 7. `make generate` 成功执行且 `git diff --exit-code` 通过\n111: 8. 单元测试通过（常量值验证、零值行为、DeepCopy 隔离）\n112: \n113: ## 状态\n114: - [ ] 提案审查\n115: - [ ] 实现\n116: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 116 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## 概述\n从 AR-001（AgentRuntime）和 AR-002（CodeInterpreter）中提取并规范化共享类型与常量，建立 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` 包中跨 CRD 复用的类型基座。\n\n## 元信息\n- **Module**: pkg/apis\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n\n## 目的\nAgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 两个 CRD 共享 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` 等类型定义。当前这些共享类型定义在 `codeinterpreter_types.go` 中，`agent_type.go` 通过同包隐式引用。本变更将共享类型与常量从具体 CRD 类型文件中解耦，形成独立的 `shared_types.go` 文件，确保：\n\n1. **单一数据源** — 共享类型有且仅有一份定义，位置明确\n2. **语义清晰** — 文件名 `shared_types.go` 明确表达\"跨 CRD 共享\"的意图\n3. **可扩展性** — 后续新增 CRD（如 Workflow、Pipeline 等）可直接引用共享类型，无需重复定义或猜测类型位置\n4. **代码生成友好** — `controller-gen` 和 `k8s.io/code-generator` 对同包内的类型无感知差异，提取后不影响 DeepCopy 和 client-go 生成\n\n## 范围\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775812869215,"end":1775812869236}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775812870498,"sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","part":{"id":"prt_d76b1fccf001qp7CSGE9zgRV3a","messageID":"msg_d76b1f12c001qvnaDsewV5XSgC","sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_2dd0f5d0fdd44389b9e41f75","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Define shared types and constants in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` that are reused across AgentRuntime (AR-001) and CodeInterpreter (AR-002) CRD type definitions, establishing a single source of truth for port configuration, protocol enumeration, and authentication mode types.\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: ProtocolType enumeration\n10: \n11: The system SHALL define `ProtocolType` as a typed string constant with values `HTTP` and `HTTPS`, serving as the protocol enumeration for sandbox port configuration.\n12: \n13: #### Scenario: ProtocolType constants have correct values\n14: - **GIVEN** the constants `ProtocolTypeHTTP` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` are defined\n15: - **WHEN** their values are inspected\n16: - **THEN** `ProtocolTypeHTTP` SHALL equal `\"HTTP\"` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` SHALL equal `\"HTTPS\"`\n17: \n18: #### Scenario: ProtocolType underlying type is string\n19: - **GIVEN** the `ProtocolType` type definition\n20: - **WHEN** the underlying type is inspected\n21: - **THEN** it SHALL be `string`, enabling JSON serialization without custom marshalers\n22: \n23: ### Requirement: AuthModeType enumeration\n24: \n25: The system SHALL define `AuthModeType` as a typed string constant with values `picod` and `none`, serving as the authentication mode enumeration for sandbox configuration.\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: AuthModeType constants have correct values\n28: - **GIVEN** the constants `AuthModePicoD` and `AuthModeNone` are defined\n29: - **WHEN** their values are inspected\n30: - **THEN** `AuthModePicoD` SHALL equal `\"picod\"` and `AuthModeNone` SHALL equal `\"none\"`\n31: \n32: #### Scenario: AuthModeType underlying type is string\n33: - **GIVEN** the `AuthModeType` type definition\n34: - **WHEN** the underlying type is inspected\n35: - **THEN** it SHALL be `string`, enabling JSON serialization without custom marshalers\n36: \n37: ### Requirement: TargetPort struct\n38: \n39: The system SHALL define `TargetPort` as a struct with fields for URL path prefix (`PathPrefix`), port name (`Name`), port number (`Port`), and protocol (`Protocol`), with appropriate JSON tags for Kubernetes CRD serialization.\n40: \n41: #### Scenario: TargetPort serializes with correct JSON keys\n42: - **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` instance with all fields populated\n43: - **WHEN** the struct is serialized to JSON\n44: - **THEN** the output SHALL use camelCase keys: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`\n45: \n46: #### Scenario: TargetPort omits empty optional fields\n47: - **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` with only `Port` set to `8080`\n48: - **WHEN** the struct is serialized to JSON\n49: - **THEN** `pathPrefix`, `name`, and `protocol` SHALL be omitted from the output (omitempty behavior)\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: TargetPort Port field is required\n52: - **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` struct definition\n53: - **WHEN** the JSON tags are inspected\n54: - **THEN** `Port` SHALL NOT have `omitempty`, making it a required field in CRD validation\n55: \n56: ### Requirement: Single source of truth\n57: \n58: The system SHALL define `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`, and `TargetPort` exactly once in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`, with both AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter types referencing these shared definitions rather than duplicating them.\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: No duplicate type definitions\n61: - **GIVEN** the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` package\n62: - **WHEN** the package is compiled\n63: - **THEN** there SHALL be exactly one definition each of `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`, and `TargetPort`\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime references shared types\n66: - **GIVEN** the `agent_type.go` file\n67: - **WHEN** the type definitions are inspected\n68: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeSpec` SHALL reference the shared `TargetPort` type for its port configuration\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter references shared types\n71: - **GIVEN** the `codeinterpreter_types.go` file\n72: - **WHEN** the type definitions are inspected\n73: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` SHALL reference the shared `TargetPort` type for its `Ports` field\n74: \n75: ### Requirement: DeepCopy generation for TargetPort\n76: \n77: The system SHALL generate `DeepCopy` and `DeepCopyInto` methods for `TargetPort` via `controller-gen object`, ensuring safe cross-goroutine value copying.\n78: \n79: #### Scenario: DeepCopy methods exist for TargetPort\n80: - **GIVEN** `make generate` has been run\n81: - **WHEN** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` is inspected\n82: - **THEN** it SHALL contain `DeepCopyInto` and `DeepCopy` methods for `TargetPort`\n83: \n84: #### Scenario: DeepCopy produces independent copies\n85: - **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` with `Name` set to `\"web\"`\n86: - **WHEN** `DeepCopy()` is called and the copy's `Name` is modified\n87: - **THEN** the original's `Name` SHALL remain `\"web\"` (no shared references)\n88: \n89: ### Requirement: Build and test integrity\n90: \n91: The system SHALL compile cleanly and pass all unit tests for the shared types.\n92: \n93: #### Scenario: Package compiles\n94: - **GIVEN** Go toolchain and all dependencies are available\n95: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/apis/...` is executed\n96: - **THEN** the command SHALL exit with code 0 and produce no errors\n97: \n98: #### Scenario: Unit tests pass\n99: - **GIVEN** the test files `codeinterpreter_types_test.go`, `agent_type_test.go`, `register_test.go`, and `groupversion_info_test.go` exist\n100: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` is executed\n101: - **THEN** all tests SHALL pass, including `ProtocolType` constant tests, `AuthModeType` constant tests, `TargetPort` zero-value/full-field tests, scheme registration tests, and GroupVersion constant tests\n102: \n103: ### Requirement: GroupVersion and SchemeBuilder\n104: \n105: The system SHALL define `GroupVersion` as `schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`, a `SchemeBuilder` using `scheme.Builder`, and `AddToScheme` as the builder's add function.\n106: \n107: #### Scenario: GroupVersion has correct group and version\n108: - **GIVEN** the `GroupVersion` constant in `groupversion_info.go`\n109: - **WHEN** its fields are inspected\n110: - **THEN** `GroupVersion.Group` SHALL equal `\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"` and `GroupVersion.Version` SHALL equal `\"v1alpha1\"`\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: SchemeBuilder is configured with GroupVersion\n113: - **GIVEN** the `SchemeBuilder` variable\n114: - **WHEN** its GroupVersion is inspected\n115: - **THEN** it SHALL equal `GroupVersion`\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: AddToScheme delegates to SchemeBuilder\n118: - **GIVEN** the `AddToScheme` variable\n119: - **WHEN** it is compared to `SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme`\n120: - **THEN** they SHALL be the same function\n121: \n122: ### Requirement: Kind and GroupVersionKind constants\n123: \n124: The system SHALL define kind constants (`CodeInterpreterKind`, `CodeInterpreterListKind`, `AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeListKind`) and GroupVersionKind constants (`CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind`, `CodeInterpreterGroupKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`) in `register.go`.\n125: \n126: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter kind constants are correct\n127: - **GIVEN** the constants in `register.go`\n128: - **WHEN** they are inspected\n129: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterKind` SHALL equal `\"CodeInterpreter\"`, `CodeInterpreterListKind` SHALL equal `\"CodeInterpreterList\"`, and `CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind` SHALL equal `GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")`\n130: \n131: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime kind constants are correct\n132: - **GIVEN** the constants in `register.go`\n133: - **WHEN** they are inspected\n134: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeKind` SHALL equal `\"AgentRuntime\"`, `AgentRuntimeListKind` SHALL equal `\"AgentRuntimeList\"`, and `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind` SHALL equal `GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")`\n135: \n136: #### Scenario: SchemeGroupVersion aliases GroupVersion\n137: - **GIVEN** the `SchemeGroupVersion` variable in `register.go`\n138: - **WHEN** it is compared to `GroupVersion`\n139: - **THEN** they SHALL be equal\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: Resource helper returns correct GroupVersionResource\n142: - **GIVEN** the `Resource(resource string)` helper function\n143: - **WHEN** called with `\"agentruntimes\"`\n144: - **THEN** it SHALL return `schema.GroupVersionResource{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\"}`\n145: \n146: #### Scenario: Resource helper works for codeinterpreters\n147: - **GIVEN** the `Resource(resource string)` helper function\n148: - **WHEN** called with `\"codeinterpreters\"`\n149: - **THEN** it SHALL return `schema.GroupVersionResource{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"codeinterpreters\"}`\n\n(End of file - total 149 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine shared types and constants in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` that are reused across AgentRuntime (AR-001) and CodeInterpreter (AR-002) CRD type definitions, establishing a single source of truth for port configuration, protocol enumeration, and authentication mode types.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: ProtocolType enumeration\n\nThe system SHALL define `ProtocolType` as a typed string constant with values `HTTP` and `HTTPS`, serving as the protocol enumeration for sandbox port configuration.\n\n#### Scenario: ProtocolType constants have correct values\n- **GIVEN** the constants `ProtocolTypeHTTP` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` are defined\n- **WHEN** their values are inspected\n- **THEN** `ProtocolTypeHTTP` SHALL equal `\"HTTP\"` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` SHALL equal `\"HTTPS\"`\n\n#### Scenario: ProtocolType underlying type is string\n- **GIVEN** the `ProtocolType` type definition\n- **WHEN** the underlying type is inspected","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775812870488,"end":1775812870496}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775812871864,"sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","part":{"id":"prt_d76b201f4001lQd0haumaB6hM8","messageID":"msg_d76b1f12c001qvnaDsewV5XSgC","sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_54f8876e677748459c857749","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-1 (Proposal)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: S\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## T-001: 创建 shared_types.go — 共享类型与常量定义\n11: \n12: - [ ] T-001.01 定义 `type ProtocolType string`\n13: - [ ] T-001.02 定义常量 `ProtocolTypeHTTP ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"` 和 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"`\n14: - [ ] T-001.03 定义 `type AuthModeType string`\n15: - [ ] T-001.04 定义常量 `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"` 和 `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n16: - [ ] T-001.05 定义 `type TargetPort struct`，字段：`PathPrefix string`、`Name string`、`Port uint32`、`Protocol ProtocolType`\n17: - [ ] T-001.06 所有字段使用正确的 JSON tag（camelCase: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`）\n18: - [ ] T-001.07 `Port` 字段不带 `omitempty`（必填），其余可选字段带 `omitempty`\n19: \n20: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`；`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`；`TargetPort` JSON 序列化正确\n21: \n22: ---\n23: \n24: ## T-002: 编写单元测试 — 常量值验证\n25: \n26: - [ ] T-002.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types_test.go`\n27: - [ ] T-002.02 测试 `TestProtocolTypeConstants`：验证 `ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`ProtocolTypeHTTPS == \"HTTPS\"`\n28: - [ ] T-002.03 测试 `TestAuthModeTypeConstants`：验证 `AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`、`AuthModeNone == \"none\"`\n29: \n30: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestProtocolTypeConstants -v` 通过；`-run TestAuthModeTypeConstants -v` 通过\n31: \n32: ---\n33: \n34: ## T-003: 编写单元测试 — TargetPort 零值与全字段测试\n35: \n36: - [ ] T-003.01 测试 `TestTargetPortZeroValues`：验证仅设置 `Port` 时其他字段为零值\n37: - [ ] T-003.02 测试 `TestTargetPortWithAllFields`：验证所有字段赋值后正确读取\n38: \n39: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestTargetPort -v` 通过\n40: \n41: ---\n42: \n43: ## T-004: 生成 DeepCopy 方法\n44: \n45: - [ ] T-004.01 运行 `make generate`（或 `controller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/...\"`）\n46: - [ ] T-004.02 验证 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 已更新，包含 `TargetPort` 的 DeepCopy 方法\n47: - [ ] T-004.03 验证 `git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n48: \n49: **验收**: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 存在且包含 `TargetPort` DeepCopy；`go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## T-005: 全量验证门禁\n54: \n55: - [ ] T-005.01 `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n56: - [ ] T-005.02 `go test ./pkg/apis/... -v` 全部通过\n57: - [ ] T-005.03 `ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType`、`TargetPort` 在包中有且仅有一份定义\n58: - [ ] T-005.04 `make generate` 成功且 `git diff --exit-code` 通过\n59: - [ ] T-005.05 常量值正确：`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`\n60: \n61: **验收**: 全部检查项通过，AR-003 可标记为完成\n\n(End of file - total 61 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 任务清单\n\n> **Stage**: ST-1 (Proposal)\n> **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n> **Language**: Go\n> **Size**: S\n\n---\n\n## T-001: 创建 shared_types.go — 共享类型与常量定义\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 定义 `type ProtocolType string`\n- [ ] T-001.02 定义常量 `ProtocolTypeHTTP ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"` 和 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"`\n- [ ] T-001.03 定义 `type AuthModeType string`\n- [ ] T-001.04 定义常量 `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"` 和 `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n- [ ] T-001.05 定义 `type TargetPort struct`，字段：`PathPrefix string`、`Name string`、`Port uint32`、`Protocol ProtocolType`\n- [ ] T-001.06 所有字段使用正确的 JSON tag（camelCase: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`）\n- [ ] T-001.07 `Port` 字段不带 `omitempty`（必填），其余可选字段带 `omitempty`\n\n**验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`；`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`；`TargetPort` JSON 序列化正确","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775812871856,"end":1775812871863}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775812873163,"sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","part":{"id":"prt_d76b2073f001zaSGyU7hU1qqZq","messageID":"msg_d76b1f12c001qvnaDsewV5XSgC","sessionID":"ses_2894e2838ffel457jblvWgAD6s","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_4313a58a87fb42ffb107abba","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量 — 设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位\n6: \n7: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中的共享类型与常量是 AgentCube 所有 CRD（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 及未来新增 CRD）的类型基座。它们定义了跨 CRD 复用的端口配置、协议枚举和认证模式，确保整个 API 层的一致性和可维护性。\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 包结构\n10: \n11: ```\n12: pkg/apis/\n13: └── runtime/\n14:     └── v1alpha1/\n15:         ├── doc.go                      # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n16:         ├── groupversion_info.go        # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n17:         ├── register.go                 # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n18:         ├── shared_types.go             # 共享类型与常量（本变更核心）\n19:         ├── shared_types_test.go        # 共享类型测试\n20:         ├── agent_type.go               # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义 (AR-001)\n21:         ├── codeinterpreter_types.go    # CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义 (AR-002)\n22:         └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go    # controller-gen object 自动生成\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ### 1.3 依赖关系\n26: \n27: ```\n28: 共享类型与常量\n29:   ├── k8s.io/apimachinery (无外部依赖，纯 Go 类型)\n30:   │\n31:   ├──→ AgentRuntime 类型引用 TargetPort、ProtocolType\n32:   ├──→ CodeInterpreter 类型引用 TargetPort、ProtocolType、AuthModeType\n33:   └──→ make generate 产出 TargetPort 的 DeepCopy 方法\n34: ```\n35: \n36: ---\n37: \n38: ## 2. 数据结构\n39: \n40: ### 2.1 ProtocolType 枚举\n41: \n42: ```go\n43: // ProtocolType 定义沙箱端口使用的协议类型\n44: type ProtocolType string\n45: \n46: const (\n47:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n48:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n49: )\n50: ```\n51: \n52: | 常量 | 值 | 说明 |\n53: |------|-----|------|\n54: | `ProtocolTypeHTTP` | `\"HTTP\"` | 超文本传输协议 |\n55: | `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` | `\"HTTPS\"` | 安全超文本传输协议 |\n56: \n57: ### 2.2 AuthModeType 枚举\n58: \n59: ```go\n60: // AuthModeType 定义沙箱认证模式\n61: type AuthModeType string\n62: \n63: const (\n64:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n65:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n66: )\n67: ```\n68: \n69: | 常量 | 值 | 说明 |\n70: |------|-----|------|\n71: | `AuthModePicoD` | `\"picod\"` | 使用 PicoD 认证 |\n72: | `AuthModeNone` | `\"none\"` | 无需认证 |\n73: \n74: ### 2.3 TargetPort 结构体\n75: \n76: ```go\n77: // TargetPort 定义沙箱暴露的端口配置\n78: type TargetPort struct {\n79:     PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n80:     Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n81:     Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n82:     Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n83: }\n84: ```\n85: \n86: | 字段 | 类型 | JSON tag | 必填 | 说明 |\n87: |------|------|----------|------|------|\n88: | `PathPrefix` | `string` | `pathPrefix,omitempty` | 否 | URL 路径前缀 |\n89: | `Name` | `string` | `name,omitempty` | 否 | 端口名称 |\n90: | `Port` | `uint32` | `port` | 是 | 端口号 |\n91: | `Protocol` | `ProtocolType` | `protocol` | 是 | 协议类型（HTTP/HTTPS） |\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ## 3. 测试策略\n96: \n97: ### 3.1 常量值测试\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: func TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n101:     assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTP\"), ProtocolTypeHTTP)\n102:     assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTPS\"), ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n103: }\n104: \n105: func TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n106:     assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"picod\"), AuthModePicoD)\n107:     assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"none\"), AuthModeNone)\n108: }\n109: ```\n110: \n111: ### 3.2 TargetPort 零值行为测试\n112: \n113: ```go\n114: func TestTargetPortZeroValues(t *testing.T) {\n115:     tp := TargetPort{Port: 8080}\n116:     assert.Empty(t, tp.PathPrefix)\n117:     assert.Empty(t, tp.Name)\n118:     assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"\"), tp.Protocol)\n119: }\n120: ```\n121: \n122: ### 3.3 TargetPort 全字段测试\n123: \n124: ```go\n125: func TestTargetPortWithAllFields(t *testing.T) {\n126:     tp := TargetPort{\n127:         PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n128:         Name:       \"web\",\n129:         Port:       8080,\n130:         Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTPS,\n131:     }\n132:     assert.Equal(t, \"/api\", tp.PathPrefix)\n133:     assert.Equal(t, \"web\", tp.Name)\n134:     assert.Equal(t, uint32(8080), tp.Port)\n135:     assert.Equal(t, ProtocolTypeHTTPS, tp.Protocol)\n136: }\n137: ```\n138: \n139: ---\n140: \n141: ## 4. 实现步骤\n142: \n143: ### 4.1 文件创建顺序\n144: \n145: 1. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` — 共享类型与常量定义\n146: 2. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types_test.go` — 共享类型测试\n147: 3. 运行 `make generate` — 更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`（包含 TargetPort DeepCopy）\n148: \n149: ### 4.2 验证检查清单\n150: \n151: - [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n152: - [ ] `ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType`、`TargetPort` 在包中有且仅有一份定义\n153: - [ ] 常量值正确：`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"` 等\n154: - [ ] `make generate` 成功更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n155: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/...` 全部通过\n\n(End of file - total 155 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中的共享类型与常量是 AgentCube 所有 CRD（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 及未来新增 CRD）的类型基座。它们定义了跨 CRD 复用的端口配置、协议枚举和认证模式，确保整个 API 层的一致性和可维护性。\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── doc.go                      # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n        ├── groupversion_info.go        # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n        ├── register.go                 # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n        ├── shared_types.go             # 共享类型与常量（本变更核心）\n        ├── shared_types_test.go        # 共享类型测试\n        ├── agent_type.go               # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义 (AR-001)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","time":{"start":1775812873153,"end":1775812873161}}}}
